    "2) Conversely, Expert 2 demonstrates considerable control over token allocation in the initial layers, which shifts as the model deepens.",
    "3) Expert 4 then begins to increasingly manage the tokens, reflecting a gradual assumption of responsibilities.",
    "4) Expert 3 also contributes to token handling as the model progresses, illustrating collaborative task division among the experts.",
    "These behaviours suggest that the experts in Uni-MoE have developed a specific pattern for dividing tasks, particularly notable between Experts 2 and 4.",
